  <brief_title>Effective Use of Respiratory Patterns in the First Period of Labor in Control of Maternal Anxiety</brief_title>
  <official_title>EFFECTIVE USE OF RESPIRATORY PATTERNS IN THE FIRST PERIOD OF LABOR IN CONTROL OF MATERNAL ANXIETY: A CLINICAL TRIAL</official_title>
