  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The effectiveness of breathing exercise on anxiety in women during the first period of labor.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The groups will be randomized into intervention groups, which will be held ventilatory
      patterns while the control group will receive routine care service. The measurements will be
      made during the admission, and every 2 hours until the final phase of dilation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
